                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7554" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0511</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1900 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“知而不言”到“知无不言”：天格地板“提案”文化的塑造之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Knowing Without Saying&quot; to &quot;Knowing Without Saying&quot;: The Road to Shaping the Culture of TECLIC FLOOR &#39;s &quot;Proposal&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">符纯洁，申林青，邓阳莲，冮昊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天格地板有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天格地板；“提案”文化；“麻烦”看板；“提案”改善；高效沟通</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TECLIC FLOOR; Proposal culture; The &#39;trouble&#39; billboard; Proposal improvement; Efficient communication</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业管理层需不需要向一线员工“求谏”？如何“求谏”？本案例阐述了天格地板这一传统制造企业在总经理肖亦鸿的带领下，主动向广大一线员工“求谏”，并塑造与企业发展需要相匹配的“提案”文化的过程。自2015年以来，天格从实施365改善、“麻烦”看板到“提案”改善制度，大胆实践“提案”文化并敢于创新，经历了多次改革，最终在组织内部培育出浓厚的员工建言献策氛围，充分发挥出了“提案”文化对本土员工从“知而不言”到“知无不言”的正向引导作用。天格的“提案”文化实践，为我国本土企业培育一线员工的主动建言献策行为提供了一种有效参考，为企业打造自下而上的高效沟通反馈系统，助力企业降本增效提供了一个有价值的样本。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Do enterprise management need to &quot;seek advice&quot; from front line employees? How to &quot;seek advice&quot;? This case illustrates the process of TECLIC FLOOR, a traditional manufacturing enterprise, actively seeking advice from front line employees under the leadership of General Manager Xiao Yihong, and shaping a &quot;proposal&quot; culture that matches the development needs of the enterprise. Since 2015, TECLIC has gone through multiple reforms, boldly practicing the &quot;proposal&quot; culture and daring to innovate, from implementing the &quot;365 improvement&quot; and &quot;trouble&quot; signboard to the &quot;proposal&quot; improvement system. Ultimately, it has cultivated a strong atmosphere of employee advice and suggestions within the organization, fully demonstrating the positive guiding role of the &quot;proposal&quot; culture in guiding local employees from &quot;knowing but not speaking&quot; to &quot;knowing without saying&quot;. The cultural practice of TECLIC&#39;s &quot;proposal&quot; provides an effective reference for local enterprises in China to cultivate proactive and constructive behavior among frontline employees, and provides a valuable sample for enterprises to create a bottom-up and efficient feedback system to help reduce costs and increase efficiency.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业文化》、《战略人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织文化变革的前因动力模型；企业文化的结构；企业文化设计；PDCA循环理论；企业文化的功能；领导者对企业文化的能动作用</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
